Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的敵人 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「突擊加速」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Assault Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 第二回合 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 別過來 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時鐘停下了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡難道是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 想像自己的「對戰虛擬角色」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(786,655)}<Duel Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後喊出來 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻加速」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(648,653)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 好漂亮 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這裡是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是加速世界 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和「Brain Burst」不同 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是以與之相似的法則所支配的空間 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我知道了 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻加速」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們也來 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 「超頻加速」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(667,655)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們沒有集中 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「Call Elemental Brit」 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數量太多了啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千 用我 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 去了哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「雷霆…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千 一上來就放大招？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(620,655)}Cyan Spike> 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下來解決本體 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也過去 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(620,655)}Cyan Spike> 
