Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(620,655)}Cyan Spike> 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也… 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼這樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 得意忘形 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「飛針四射」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Splash Stinger>
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費子彈了 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那傢伙… 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「飛針四射」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,655)}<Splash Stinger>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千…子彈…子彈已經用完了… 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我稍微休息一下… 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 真是沒毅力啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春也是啊 發什麼呆啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的迴旋速度不快 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用機動力決勝負的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那點程度的話吾王… 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這點事學姐應該已經注意到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用我這種人特地過去說 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且只是注意到而已 也沒什麼對策… 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要廢話了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去學姐那裡啊 小春 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐也是女孩子啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會希望讓男孩子緊緊拉住 提供建議 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就…就算你這麼說… 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千 左邊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會讓你跑掉啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千 上面 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 只要學姐也能在空中自在地行動的話 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 小春 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話 不會再讓你吃我媽媽做的飯了 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 謝謝 小千 阿拓 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春雪？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙光靠物理攻擊力無法戰勝 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是需要快速瞄準他攻擊時的空隙 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是要瞄準她會減速的迴旋啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是學姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要怎麼做 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算這裡是低重力 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空中的話她會比較強 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來成為學姐的羽翼 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以幸…學姐就集中於物理攻擊吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終於看著我說話了啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼小的羽翼不怎麼靠得住 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個空間也和「Brain Burst」一樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像力 「心念」是有效的 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 想像就會成為力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你期望著什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在 所期望的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和學姐一起飛翔 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧 學姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個真厲害啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的羽翼飛翔… 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼美好的事嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能結束了 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾王 這是… 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空間正在崩潰 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大門…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:22:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千 我快到極限了 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快沒汽油了 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.93,0:23:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 再加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真愛亂使喚人阿 真是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油 
Comment: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個… 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.68,0:23:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想那個人的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.65,0:23:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「DShK」的事 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很悲傷 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.91,0:23:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在誰都不會來的伺服器中 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.05,0:23:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直等著對戰的對手 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.60,0:23:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後就像是沒有人氣的遊戲結束運營時一樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打倒她的時候 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了遊戲通關之後的 滿足與寂寞 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定也是一樣的 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的話就好了 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.29,0:24:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說回來 春雪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個最後的合體 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.33,0:24:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是想挑戰什麼 但是放棄了 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.62,0:24:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}所以幸…學姐就… 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.15,0:24:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.95,0:24:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是那個情況下的勢氣… 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.50,0:24:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者說是試膽… 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.83,0:24:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.46,0:24:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有一天 有了那種自信的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.74,0:24:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我叫吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.92,0:24:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用真正的名字 叫學姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.98,0:24:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 我就是黑雪公主 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.57,0:24:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Comment: 0,0:25:03.52,0:25:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.52,0:25:06.87,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.87,0:25:10.70,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.70,0:25:12.33,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}Wake up your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.38,0:25:14.33,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}Flashed in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.45,0:25:16.83,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}It's a 「Burst」 of sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.83,0:25:23.11,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「諦め」がくれた 安楽 沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.17,0:25:26.11,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}いつからだっただろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.18,0:25:29.20,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.23,0:25:32.55,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}-変わらずにいてと願うこと-
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.55,0:25:36.21,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}-変わりゆく時に生きる僕ら-
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.27,0:25:39.38,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}本当の声を…言い得ぬ夢を…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.38,0:25:41.67,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}君と繋がった空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.77,0:25:43.65,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}響かせて！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.17,0:25:47.61,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}もっと強く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.73,0:25:50.94,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.03,0:25:54.26,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「今度こそは…」 つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.36,0:25:57.52,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}傷さえも無駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.59,0:26:00.82,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.90,0:26:04.04,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.12,0:26:07.37,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}歪む世界 走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.43,0:26:10.61,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}感覚のその向うへ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.71,0:26:16.21,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「真実」と 加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.52,0:25:06.87,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}我們遭受淚水與傷痛煩心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.87,0:25:10.70,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}而我被置身於那亂於無數未來的競爭之中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.70,0:25:12.33,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}將自身覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.38,0:25:14.33,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}閃現於高空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.45,0:25:16.83,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}這就是「加速」快感
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.83,0:25:23.11,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「放棄」帶來的安樂停滯世界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.17,0:25:26.11,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}何時悄然而至的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.18,0:25:29.20,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}恍然間光輝耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.23,0:25:32.55,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}祈求永恆無變
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.55,0:25:36.21,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}我們卻生活在幻化無常的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.27,0:25:39.38,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}搭載著吐露的真聲與難以言說的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.38,0:25:41.67,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}與你一同展翅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.77,0:25:43.65,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}讓聲音迴蕩在天際！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.17,0:25:47.61,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}更加的堅強…用雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.73,0:25:50.94,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}將淚水全部抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.03,0:25:54.26,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}喃喃而道「下次一定…」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.36,0:25:57.52,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}不會讓傷痛僅僅成為過往
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.59,0:26:00.82,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}更加快速地…到達你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.90,0:26:04.04,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}即使羽翼已支離破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.12,0:26:07.37,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}仍會奔跑在這個扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.43,0:26:10.61,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}依循著感覺的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.71,0:26:16.21,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}與「真實」一同加速
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.31,0:25:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,